<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('partials/head') %>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <main>
        <div class="container-custom py-12 md:py-20">
            <header class="text-center mb-16">
                <h1 class="title font-cormorant text-5xl md:text-7xl text-accent-purple mb-4 font-medium">Vagus Nerve Live Workshop!</h1>
                <p class="subtitle font-cormorant text-2xl md:text-3xl text-gold leading-tight">Join Us for a Transformative Experience</p>
            </header>

            <section class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto text-center mb-12">
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-8">Join the Vagus Skool for our Live Vagus Nerve Stimulation Workshops! We host regular interactive sessions to help you master these transformative techniques.</p>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed font-medium text-accent-purple">We would love to have you join us live! Please check our community calendar below to see all upcoming workshop dates and times.</p>
            </section>

            <div class="text-center mb-16 bg-white/30 backdrop-blur-sm p-10 rounded-3xl border border-accent-purple/10 max-w-2xl mx-auto shadow-sm">
                <h2 class="font-cormorant text-3xl md:text-4xl text-accent-purple font-medium mb-4">Stay Connected</h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-dark-text opacity-90 mb-8">All live events, workshops, and community calls are listed on our official Skool calendar. Bring your VNS tools and your questions!</p>
                
                <button id="calendar-button" class="golden-button w-full md:w-auto">
                    View Workshop Calendar
                </button>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
                <p class="text-accent-purple text-sm md:text-base opacity-90">Join our growing community and start your healing journey today.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script>
        // Calendar button click handler
        document.getElementById('calendar-button').addEventListener('click', () => {
            window.location.href = 'https://www.skool.com/vagus/calendar';
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
